{"tid":513092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲人拆禮物日通宵排隊掃平貨　開門始知無折扣　主播恥笑不停","createTime":"2017-12-29T07:39:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T08:16:53.000Z","uid":72478,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"800b8fb9033829b63092c6e71385e2811dab442d","tid":513092,"uid":72478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T07:39:40.000Z","msg":"影片：<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/144308\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F144308&d=HT%2BmosxtFQmebK13LlDiktr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=10a843cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/144308</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/144308/thumbnail/e29506bfb3a08b8fd649d4036b33f134.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F144308%2Fthumbnail%2Fe29506bfb3a08b8fd649d4036b33f134.jpg&h=74da3427&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n澳洲的零售商傳統上都會在拆禮物日舉行減價日，總會吸引民眾掃貨。而在當地時間周二（12月26日）早上，悉尼旺區皮特街（Pitt Street）一間時裝店外，有一條長達200米的人龍，大家都等待舖頭在早上8時開門時，立即搶購心頭好。有市民表示，早在聖誕節晚上9時已在排隊，亦有人在凌晨3、4時來到，即使大家飲了數杯咖啡提神，雙眼的黑眼圈嚴重浮現都沒所謂，總之希望感受到這種在節目瘋狂購物的氣氛。<br />\n<br />\n正當人們認為，等得又餓又累都是值得之際，有部分店舖清早開門營業，顧客才驚覺所有貨品仍以正價出售。澳洲廣播公司的記者甚至站在名店Gucci門外，直言不明白為什麼顧客沒有優惠都要排隊，與主播笑得合不攏嘴。<br />\n<br />\n《澳洲人報》指出，時尚名牌Gucci和LV都沒有在Boxing Day這天提供減價優惠。<br />\n<br />\n但正如澳洲廣播公司的記者指出，雖然民眾感到中伏，但仍然沒減少購物興致，不少人最後都滿載而歸。<br />\n<br />\n「我排了一整晚，雖然很累，而且之後還要上班，我仍會堅持到成功購物為止，或者這是購物的快感吧！」&mdash;&mdash;一名通宵在店舖外排隊的悉尼市民"},{"pid":"df70585bacd4a69d57729dea06084823d3fcd1b2","tid":513092,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T07:41:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"509b9082af96c4e52d20e852adbd96ed3f58c6aa","tid":513092,"uid":139816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T07:41:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cee4b6f64301cceaaec3dd90ab8710818df4ea3","tid":513092,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T07:42:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d787f739ec17aa54e6d3442e45d51cc0ca3940f","tid":513092,"uid":133529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T07:43:21.000Z","msg":"係我就返屋企啦，白排隊，俾正價"},{"pid":"feb3a808851b7f85f57606b766f00f3f423ba23c","tid":513092,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T07:46:36.000Z","msg":"下年用手機吹話有折，又再撚一次"},{"pid":"798294a87fc8e954c44a53d00eff0628d34738a7","tid":513092,"uid":37820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T07:47:43.000Z","msg":"拆禮物日<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4057baa12cc5948446b0c07c3c7a9ff9e2de57e1","tid":513092,"uid":5267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T08:05:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"948e69d5ce2b8954358a5ccc396546f1280a5e0c","tid":513092,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T08:16:53.000Z","msg":"根據連登某d人所講<br />\n佢地肯定係香港人啦<br />\n同支那人無分別"}]}